    "Then they went along through the wilderness, and compassed the land of <span class=\"person\">Edom</span>, and the land of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>, and came by the east side of the land of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>, and pitched on the other side of Arnon, but came not within the border of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>: for Arnon was the border of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>.",
