    "And it came to pass, when they saw him, that they brought thirty companions to be with him.",
    "And <span class=\"person\">Samson</span> said unto them, I will now put forth a riddle unto you: if ye can certainly declare it me within the seven days of the feast, and find it out, then I will give you thirty sheets and thirty change of garments:",
    "But if ye cannot declare it me, then shall ye give me thirty sheets and thirty change of garments. And they said unto him, Put forth thy riddle, that we may hear it.",
