    "Then three thousand men of <span class=\"person\">Judah</span> went to the top of the rock Etam, and said to <span class=\"person\">Samson</span>, Knowest thou not that the Philistines are rulers over us? what is this that thou hast done unto us? And he said unto them, As they did unto me, so have I done unto them.",
