    "And the people the men of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> encouraged themselves, and set their battle again in array in the place where they put themselves in array the first day.",
    "(And the children of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> went up and wept before the LORD until even, and asked counsel of the LORD, saying, Shall I go up again to battle against the children of <span class=\"person\">Benjamin</span> my brother? And the LORD said, Go up against him.)",
