    "And when the men of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> retired in the battle, <span class=\"person\">Benjamin</span> began to smite and kill of the men of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> about thirty persons: for they said, Surely they are smitten down before us, as in the first battle.",
